Utterance.UttText: In Bed 6, we have Roger Thompson, 49 yrs old under Dr Gordon, came in with nausea and dizziness.
He just came in the ward not too long ago and I have just done his admission papers.
His obs are all good and he complained of nausea and I have him some ondansetron 4 mg with good effect. he is on general diet but he didn't eat much due to nausea.
He is self caring and ambulant and he is resting in bed at the moment.
